<placeName cert="high">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Ζήνωνι χαίρειν Κάλλιππος. <choice><corr>ἐπικοιμᾶι</corr><sic>επι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear>ωι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αι</supplied></sic></choice> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σὺ</supplied> περιορῶν <add place="supralinear">με</add> ἐν τῶι <choice><corr>δεσμωτηρίωι</corr><sic>δεζμωτηριωι</sic></choice>; φρόντισον περὶ 

    <lb n="2"/><add place="supralinear">τῶν</add> <choice><corr>κτηνῶν</corr><sic>κτενεων</sic></choice> τῶν ὑμετέρων. γίνωσκε <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὲ ὅτι, ἐὰν ἐν</supplied>ταῦθα ὦσι αἱ αἶγες αἱ τοῦ Δημητρίου, ἀπολοῦν-

    <lb n="3"/>ται· ἱκανὴ γάρ ἐστιν <choice><corr>ἡ</corr><sic>ε</sic></choice> ὁδὸς ἣν κατά<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">γει εἰς τ</supplied>ὰς νομὰς <add place="supralinear"><choice><corr>ἀπορρῆξαι</corr><sic>απορεξαι</sic></choice> αὐτάς.</add> φρόντισον καὶ περὶ τοῦ <choice><corr>χόρτου</corr><sic>χουρτου</sic></choice> τοῦ 

    <lb n="4"/>κεκομμένου ἐν Σεναρύ, ὅπως ἂν μὴ ἀπόληται· <choice><corr>οὐ</corr><sic>ο</sic></choice> μικρὸν γάρ ἐστιν ὃ <choice><corr>ὠφεληθήσει</corr><sic>ωφεληθησι</sic></choice>· ὑπολαμβάνω 

    <lb n="5"/>ἔσεσθαι <choice><corr>δέσμας</corr><sic>δεζμας</sic></choice> εἰς <num value="3000">Γ</num>. δέομαί σου καὶ <choice><corr>ἱκετεύω</corr><sic>ικετεω</sic></choice>, μὴ περιίδης <choice><corr>με</corr><sic>μη</sic></choice> ἐν τῶι <choice><corr>δεσμωτηρίωι</corr><sic>δεζμωτηριωι</sic></choice>. ἱκανῶς 

    <lb n="6"/>βέβλαμαι ἀφ᾽ οὗ <choice><corr>ἀπῆγμαι</corr><sic>ἀπε̂γμαι</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ἀπό</corr><sic>απ</sic></choice> τοῦ κλήρου <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὗ ἐ</supplied>μισθωσάμην ἐπὶ <choice><corr>σοὶ</corr><sic>σωι</sic></choice> πεποιθώς. <choice><corr>οὐκ</corr><sic>οκ</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ὀλίγα</corr><sic>ιλια</sic></choice> <add place="supralinear">βέ</add>βλα-

    <lb n="7"/>ψαι ἀφ᾽ οὗ <choice><corr>ἀπῆγμαι</corr><sic>απεγμαι</sic></choice>, καὶ τὰ προβάτια ἃ <choice><corr>περιπεποίημαι</corr><sic>περιπεπωιημαι</sic></choice> ἀφ᾽ οὗ ἐλήλυθα πρὸς ὑμᾶς <choice><corr>διήρπα-

    <lb n="8"/>κται</corr><sic>διερπακται</sic></choice> ὑπὸ τῶν ποιμένων ἀφ᾽ οὗ <choice><corr>ἀπῆγμαι</corr><sic>απεγμαι</sic></choice>. <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear>ἰ δέ <add place="supralinear"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>ι<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></add> <choice><corr>σοι</corr><sic>σωι</sic></choice> φαίνεται, <choice><corr>καταλείψω</corr><sic>καταλιψω</sic></choice> τὴν γυναῖκα ἐν 

    <lb n="9"/>τῶι δεσμωτηρίωι περὶ ἐμοῦ, ἕως ἂν ἐπισκέψῃ περὶ ὧν <choice><corr>μοι</corr><sic>μωι</sic></choice> ἐνκαλοῦσι. 

    <lb n="10"/>εὐτύχει. </ab></div><div n="meta.1986" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.1986" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-226" notBefore="-275" type="textDate">Mitte III v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.1986" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Mich.</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">87</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">1986</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0163</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">87</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0163;1;87" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.1986" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">220</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">128</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.1986" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.1986" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Bagnall &amp; Derow, The Hellenistic Period (2004), Nr. 127.</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="fr"><head lang="de">Französisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Orrieux, Les papyrus de Zenon (1983), S. 116</bibl><bibl type="translations">Clarysse - Vandorpe, Zenon (1995), S. 102</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.1986" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="low" type="ancientFindspot">Arsinoites</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.1986" pa